'''NGC 4639'''是一個位於[[室女座|室女座]]的[[棒旋星系|棒旋星系]]，距離地球約7000萬光年，是[[室女座星系團|室女座星系團]]的成員星系之一。該星系中心有[[超大質量黑洞|超大質量黑洞]]存在<ref>{{cite news|last1=Botkin-Kowacki|first1=Eva|title=Spectacular Hubble photo: A bright galaxy holds a hidden secret|url=http://www.csmonitor.com/Science/2015/1013/Spectacular-Hubble-photo-A-bright-galaxy-holds-a-hidden-secret|accessdate=14 October 2015|work=The Christian Science Monitor|date=13 October 2015|archive-date=2017-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170830103703/https://www.csmonitor.com/Science/2015/1013/Spectacular-Hubble-photo-A-bright-galaxy-holds-a-hidden-secret|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

